title: O'NEILL HEAT 2013/14
description:
The Heat is stuffed with high-end features and materials: Built with 100% of our ultra gooey UltraFlex DS Neoprene. UltraFlex Firewall in the chest and back make this suit warmer and more flexible than previous years. The Heat also includes exterior Fluid Seam Weld, redesigned zipper panel, Covert Code Red Zipper, clean graphics and 
easy-in-easy-out usability.
